{"tid":124892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽聞大哥被暗殺亡　傳金正恩痛哭抽搐","createTime":"2017-02-18T04:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T01:04:44.000Z","uid":1886,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be03ebf8628c3e6b02622bda31a13cdc4211ffb8","tid":124892,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:12:05.000Z","msg":"聽聞大哥被暗殺亡　傳金正恩痛哭抽搐<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170218/1058946/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170218%2F1058946%2F&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDctr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0c5c55da\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170218/1058946/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170218/640_517fec845336ac49a581de1edc101b0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170218%2F640_517fec845336ac49a581de1edc101b0d.jpg&h=b264763d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓最高領導人金正恩大哥金正男在馬來西亞遇刺身亡，雖說外界傳言這道刺殺令很可能是金正恩指示的，但現在有另一個消息傳出，稱金正恩聽聞大哥被刺殺身亡後，當場癱軟在沙發上，痛哭了一夜，嘴角抽搐。<br />\n<br />\n據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，北韓有媒體稱金正恩得知大哥被刺身亡後，恍惚了好幾個小時才反應過來，然後放聲大哭，悲傷到不能自己，更形容他「癱倒在沙發上，雙眼無神，臉色蠟黃，嘴角伴隨一陣陣地抽搐」。北韓媒體也說，金正恩痛哭一夜後喉嚨沙啞，第2天早上甚至因此無法主持會議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金正恩雙眼無神，臉色蠟黃，嘴角伴隨一陣陣地抽搐。<br />\n<br />\n但這並非首次金正恩被報導因親人去世而痛哭，先前他的姑丈張成澤被處決後，報導也說他哭了快一周。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"052fc6e030fb9417516b6ad191c0e00e7502c9a8","tid":124892,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f5a6a16d5a7882c37e760f61aa4441c8c88a12","tid":124892,"uid":42293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:12:44.000Z